handDesc.handNote:
- ሎ has the loop marking the 7th order
                       attached directly at the body of the letter, without the horizontal
                       stroke;

- the numerals ፩ and ፬ are usually
                       difficult to
                       distinguish;

- ፮ is with the loop open, looking
                       like “compressed” ፯ (s., e.g., fol. 71rb
                       l.8);
